## Usage

#### Blade

```php
@include('sugar.bare.cell.cell', [
    'content' => '
        <h2>Hello world</h2>
    ',
    'margin' => [
        'default' => [
            'bottom' => '50'
        ],
        'mobile' => [
            'bottom' => '20'
        ]
    ]
])
```

#### Twig

```twig
{{ '{%' }} include 'sugar.bare.cell.cell' with {
    content: '<h2>Hello world</h2>',
    margin: {
        default: {
            bottom: '50'
        },
        mobile: {
            bottom: '20'
        }
    }
} {{ '%}' }}
```

